OL,4,CEntire Pride in London advisory board
OL,5,Cquits over 'hostile environment'
OL,6, All 10 members of the Pride in London
OL,7, community advisory board (CAB) have
OL,8, resigned, citing a "hostile
OL,9, environment" for volunteers of colour.
OL,11,FThey have called for new leadership and
OL,12,Ffor City Hall to investigate bullying
OL,13,Fallegations.
OL,15,FThe mayor of London said he "takes
OL,16,Fallegations of this nature extremely
OL,17,Fseriously".
OL,19,FA full review of "processes at board
OL,20,Flevel" is being carried out, Pride in
OL,21,FLondon said.
